==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Gam
<hw>Gam</hw> <pr>(g⟦acr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Gammed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Gam"ming</conjf>.]</vmorph> <fld>(Naut.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>To gather in a gam; -- said of whales.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>To engage in a gam, or (<mark>Local, U. S.</mark>) in
